<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0b1220">
<meta name="description" content="Atlas Pay — send, receive, and pay out money worldwide in seconds. Transparent fees, mid-market FX, instant transfers where rails allow, and bank-grade security.">
<title>Atlas Pay — Money that just moves</title>
<style>
  /* ---------- Tokens ---------- */
  :root {
    --bg: #f7f8fb;
    --bg-elev: #ffffff;
    --ink: #0b1220;
    --ink-2: #28324a;
    --ink-3: #5a6479;
    --line: #e5e8ef;
    --line-2: #d6dbe6;
    --brand: #1f4dff;
    --brand-ink: #ffffff;
    --brand-50: #eef1ff;
    --accent: #00c08b;
    --warn: #b25a00;
    --danger: #c0362c;
    --radius: 14px;
    --radius-sm: 10px;
    --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(11,18,32,.06), 0 1px 1px rgba(11,18,32,.04);
    --shadow-md: 0 8px 24px rgba(11,18,32,.08), 0 2px 6px rgba(11,18,32,.05);
    --maxw: 1120px;
    --gutter: clamp(16px, 4vw, 32px);
    --font-sys: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji";
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1220;
      --bg-elev: #121a2e;
      --ink: #f5f7fb;
      --ink-2: #d2d8e6;
      --ink-3: #98a1b6;
      --line: #1f2a44;
      --line-2: #2a3658;
      --brand: #6c8bff;
      --brand-50: #1a2347;
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
      --shadow-md: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
    }
  }

  /* ---------- Base ---------- */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sys);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--bg);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
  }
  img, svg { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
  a { color: var(--brand); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  :focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--brand);
    outline-offset: 2px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .skip {
    position: absolute; left: -9999px; top: 0;
    background: var(--ink); color: #fff; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .skip:focus { left: 0; }
  .container { max-width: var(--maxw); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--gutter); }
  h1, h2, h3 { color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw + 0.5rem, 3.5rem); line-height: 1.05; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.4vw + 0.5rem, 2.25rem); line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 12px; }
  h3 { font-size: 1.125rem; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  p { margin: 0 0 12px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  small { color: var(--ink-3); }

  /* ---------- Header ---------- */
  header.site {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
    backdrop-filter: saturate(140%) blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(140%) blur(8px);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 80%, transparent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    height: 64px;
  }
  .brand {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .brand-mark {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, #00c08b 100%);
    display: inline-grid; place-items: center; color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  nav.primary ul {
    display: flex; gap: 22px; list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;
  }
  nav.primary a {
    color: var(--ink-2); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.97rem;
  }
  nav.primary a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .nav-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    nav.primary { display: none; }
  }

  /* ---------- Buttons ---------- */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 18px; min-height: 44px;
    border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.97rem;
    border: 1px solid transparent; cursor: pointer; transition: transform .04s ease, background .15s ease, border-color .15s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--brand); color: var(--brand-ink); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand) 88%, black); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); border-color: var(--line-2); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--bg-elev); text-decoration: none; }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero {
    padding: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px) 0 clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px 500px at 110% -10%, rgba(31,77,255,.10), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(800px 400px at -10% 0%, rgba(0,192,139,.08), transparent 60%);
  }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 56px);
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) { .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--brand-50); color: var(--brand);
    font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand) 25%, transparent);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .eyebrow .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
  .hero p.lead { font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 56ch; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px; }
  .trust-row {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 18px 28px;
    margin-top: 28px; padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--ink-3);
  }
  .trust-row span { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .trust-row svg { color: var(--accent); flex: 0 0 auto; }

  /* ---------- Send card mock ---------- */
  .send-card {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    max-width: 420px; margin-left: auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) { .send-card { margin: 0 auto; } }
  .send-card .row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
  }
  .send-card .row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
  .send-card .label { color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 0.92rem; }
  .send-card .value { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
  .send-card .amount { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .send-card .amount-sub { color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-top: 2px; }
  .send-card .send-btn { width: 100%; margin-top: 14px; }
  .badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 15%, transparent);
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 75%, var(--ink));
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ---------- Section ---------- */
  section { padding: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px) 0; }
  section.alt { background: var(--bg-elev); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .section-head { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 0 32px; }
  .section-head p { color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 1.05rem; }

  /* ---------- Steps ---------- */
  .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .step {
    background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 22px;
  }
  .step .num {
    display: inline-grid; place-items: center; width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 8px; background: var(--brand-50); color: var(--brand);
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.92rem; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* ---------- Features ---------- */
  .features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 880px) { .features { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .feature {
    background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 22px;
  }
  .feature .icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--brand-50); color: var(--brand);
    display: grid; place-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* ---------- Fee transparency ---------- */
  .fees-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; align-items: stretch;
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) { .fees-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .fee-table {
    background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fee-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    padding: 14px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .fee-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-50) 60%, transparent); }
  .fee-row .k { color: var(--ink-2); }
  .fee-row .v { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-weight: 600; }
  .fee-note {
    background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 22px;
  }
  .fee-note ul { padding-left: 18px; margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .fee-note li { margin: 6px 0; color: var(--ink-2); }

  /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
  .faq { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
  details {
    background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }
  details + details { margin-top: 0; }
  details[open] { box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  summary {
    cursor: pointer; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  summary::after {
    content: "+"; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--ink-3);
    transition: transform .2s ease;
  }
  details[open] summary::after { content: "−"; }

  /* ---------- CTA banner ---------- */
  .cta-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4dff 0%, #00c08b 100%);
    color: #fff; border-radius: 20px; padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta-banner h2 { color: #fff; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  .cta-banner p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); margin: 0; }
  .cta-banner .btn-primary { background: #fff; color: #1f4dff; }
  .cta-banner .btn-primary:hover { background: #f0f3ff; }

  /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
  footer.site {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 32px 0 48px; margin-top: 24px;
    color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  .foot-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .foot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  .foot-grid h4 { color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 0.92rem; }
  .foot-grid ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: grid; gap: 6px; }
  .foot-grid a { color: var(--ink-2); }
  .legal { margin-top: 28px; padding-top: 18px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* ---------- Reduced motion ---------- */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    * { transition: none !important; animation: none !important; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<a class="skip" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

<header class="site" role="banner">
  <div class="container nav">
    <a class="brand" href="#" aria-label="Atlas Pay home">
      <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">A</span>
      <span>Atlas Pay</span>
    </a>
    <nav class="primary" aria-label="Primary">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#how">How it works</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#fees">Fees</a></li>
        <li><a href="#security">Security</a></li>
        <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#signin">Sign in</a>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#get-app">Get the app</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="main">

  <!-- ============== HERO ============== -->
  <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Now sending to 60+ countries</span>
        <h1 id="hero-title">Money that just moves.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Send, receive, and pay out money in seconds — across borders, banks, and currencies.
          Transparent fees. Real exchange rates. No surprises.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#get-app" aria-label="Get the Atlas Pay app">Get the app — free</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#how">See how it works</a>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-row" aria-label="Trust indicators">
          <span><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 9.3 8 11 4.6-1.7 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg> Bank-grade encryption</span>
          <span><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Licensed &amp; regulated</span>
          <span><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg> Funds available 24/7</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Live "send money" preview card -->
      <div class="send-card" role="region" aria-label="Send money preview">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
          <span class="label">You send</span>
          <span class="badge">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            Locked rate
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="amount" aria-live="polite">$<span id="send-amt">500.00</span> <small style="font-weight:500; color:var(--ink-3); font-size:1rem;">USD</small></div>
        <div class="amount-sub">Fee $1.99 · Total <span id="total-out">$501.99</span></div>

        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">Exchange rate</span>
          <span class="value" id="fx-rate">1 USD = 0.9210 EUR</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">Recipient gets</span>
          <span class="value">€<span id="recv-amt">460.50</span> EUR</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">Arrives</span>
          <span class="value" style="color:var(--accent)">In seconds</span>
        </div>

        <button class="btn btn-primary send-btn" id="send-btn" type="button" aria-describedby="send-help">
          Send now
        </button>
        <small id="send-help" style="display:block; margin-top:10px; text-align:center;">
          You'll review and confirm before any money moves.
        </small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============== HOW IT WORKS ============== -->
  <section id="how" aria-labelledby="how-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 id="how-title">Three taps to send money.</h2>
        <p>No jargon. No surprise fees. No "pending for 5 business days."</p>
      </div>
      <ol class="steps" style="list-style:none; padding:0;">
        <li class="step">
          <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
          <h3>Pick a recipient</h3>
          <p>Phone number, email, @handle, or QR. If they're not on Atlas yet, we'll invite them.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="step">
          <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
          <h3>Enter the amount</h3>
          <p>See the exact fee, exchange rate, and arrival time before you confirm.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="step">
          <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
          <h3>Confirm with your face</h3>
          <p>Face ID, Touch ID, or passkey. Done. Receipt in your inbox.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============== FEATURES ============== -->
  <section id="features" class="alt" aria-labelledby="features-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 id="features-title">Built for everyone who moves money.</h2>
        <p>Whether it's coffee with a friend or payroll for 5,000 contractors — Atlas handles it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12h18"/><path d="M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Instant transfers</h3>
          <p>Money arrives in seconds on RTP, FedNow, FPS, UPI, PIX, and SEPA Instant — with honest ETAs everywhere else.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M3 12h18"/><path d="M12 3a14 14 0 0 1 0 18M12 3a14 14 0 0 0 0 18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>40+ currencies</h3>
          <p>Hold balances in dollars, euros, pounds, rupees, reais, and more. Convert at the real mid-market rate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M3 10h18"/><path d="M7 15h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Link any card or bank</h3>
          <p>Apple&nbsp;Pay, Google&nbsp;Pay, debit, credit, or your bank account. Top up or cash out instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 7h18M3 12h18M3 17h12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Mass payouts</h3>
          <p>Pay 1 person or 50,000. CSV upload, API, or scheduled runs. Live status for every payment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-3.5-7.1"/><path d="M21 4v5h-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Refunds &amp; disputes</h3>
          <p>Sent to the wrong person? One tap to request a return. Full buyer &amp; sender protection on eligible payments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 9.3 8 11 4.6-1.7 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Locked down by default</h3>
          <p>Passkeys, biometric step-up on payouts, device trust, and 24/7 fraud monitoring on every transaction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============== FEES ============== -->
  <section id="fees" aria-labelledby="fees-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 id="fees-title">One honest fee. Always shown before you confirm.</h2>
        <p>No hidden FX margins. No "free" that turns into 4.2%. The number you see is the number you pay.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fees-grid">
        <div class="fee-table" role="table" aria-label="Atlas Pay fee summary">
          <div class="fee-row" role="row"><span class="k" role="cell">Send to friends, same currency</span><span class="v" role="cell">Free</span></div>
          <div class="fee-row" role="row"><span class="k" role="cell">Bank transfer in (ACH / SEPA / FPS)</span><span class="v" role="cell">Free</span></div>
          <div class="fee-row" role="row"><span class="k" role="cell">Debit card top-up</span><span class="v" role="cell">1.0%</span></div>
          <div class="fee-row" role="row"><span class="k" role="cell">International transfer</span><span class="v" role="cell">From 0.43% + $0.50</span></div>
